profile (order.xml), there I found this nodes:

&lt;string name=&quot;http-proxy-host&quot;&gt;&lt;/string&gt;
&lt;string name=&quot;http-proxy-port&quot;&gt;&lt;/string&gt;

I set the proxy there, I still had problems, and I set the proxy IP
instead, and it worked.
